OL,3,CFamily raise awareness of fire risks
OL,4,Cafter blaze destroyed their home
OL,6,FA mother from Basingstoke wants to
OL,7,Fraise awareness about the fire risks
OL,8,Flinked to electrical appliances after
OL,9,Fher house was destroyed by flames.
OL,11,FMandy Ebury managed to flee the home
OL,12,Fwith her son and daughter following
OL,13,Fthe blaze, but says they have been
OL,14,Ftraumatised and believe it could have
OL,15,Fbeen caused by a faulty tumble dryer.
OL,17,FThe property is unhabitable so the
OL,18,Ffamily are being housed in temporary
OL,19,Faccommodation.
