OL,6,FAt the time of the fire, Mandy says
OL,7,Fflames and black smoke were engulfing
OL,8,Fthe hallway.
OL,10,FMandy Ebury said: "I had done a load
OL,11,Fof washing. Couldn't get it dry - put
OL,12,Fit in the tumble dryer. I was
OL,13,Ffinishing off a couple of little jobs
OL,14,Fin the downstairs toilet.
OL,16,F"Lola started saying, I can smell
OL,17,Fsmoke. We went out into the hallway
OL,18,Fand there were flames and black smoke.
