OL,6,F"The fire took hold so quickly and I
OL,7,Fwas so scared for my children's safety
OL,8,Fin particular, I didn't think about my
OL,9,Fown."
OL,11,FHome office figures compiled by the
OL,12,Fcharity Electrical Safety First show
OL,13,Fthat there were 135 accidental
OL,14,Felectrical fires involving white goods
OL,15,Facross the South and Thames Valley
OL,16,Fbetween 2023 and 2024, which is more
OL,17,Fthan two incidents a week.
