OL,3,CFamily raise awareness of fire risks
OL,4,Cafter blaze destroyed their home
OL,6,FGiuseppe Capanna from the Charity
OL,7,FElectrical Safety First, said: "Try
OL,8,Fnot to run these white goods overnight
OL,9,For unattended when you're not there,
OL,10,Ftry and be there when they're on.
OL,12,F"Don't plug them into extension leads,
OL,13,Fparticularly don't plug more than one
OL,14,Fdevice into an extension lead because
OL,15,Fyou will overload that extension lead.
OL,17,F"Check the wiring, make sure you have
OL,18,Fworking smoke alarms on every floor of
OL,19,Fyour house and just also make sure
OL,20,Fthey're working smoke alarms."
