OL,6,FElectrical Safety First says there are
OL,7,Fat least 1000 fires across the UK
OL,8,Fevery year linked to these sorts of
OL,9,Fdomestic appliances.
OL,11,FMandy's husband wasn't home when this
OL,12,Fhappened last November, but her son,
OL,13,Fwho is autistic was. Her daughter Lola
OL,14,FEbury says she has had nightmares
OL,15,Fregularly since the fire.
OL,17,FLola Ebury said: "Make sure you have a
OL,18,Ffire plan especially if you have
OL,19,Fdisabled family members.
