OL,4,Cafter blaze destroyed their home
OL,6,F"I have nightmares regularly, I have
OL,7,Fto sleep with the TV on now just to
OL,8,Ffeel normal and I get anxious just
OL,9,Fbeing near the house."
OL,11,FMandy says the incident has
OL,12,Ftraumatised the family, they had the
OL,13,Ftumble dryer for a few years so didn't
OL,14,Fexpect the blaze to start.
OL,16,FThe cause of the fire is under
OL,17,Finvestigation and the family remain in
OL,18,Ftemporary accommodation.
